Lig4 is a game for 1 or 2 players. It's based on connect 4 pieces of a same color in line (horizontal, vertical or diagonals). But you have to consider the gravity will make spaces be filled down to up.

Features:
- Advanced AI for single player;
- Multiplayer mode for two players:
